{"type":"message","id":"a7c6dd65","parentId":"bdbe341a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T04:31:54.655Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_0cb97de3-2ae5-4575-a511-2f39ac637086","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[  {    \"type\": \"text\",    \"text\": \"[cron:2ca3531d-d7c2-4846-b91f-804a1e726f81 Note-taking compliance audit (10-day session review)] ## Task: Note-taking compliance audit — 10-day session review\\n\\n\nYou are running an isolated audit. Your ONLY job:\\n\\n1. Using the session-logs skill (read ~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/session-logs/SKILL.md first, use jq commands), find ALL sessio\nn JSONL files modified in the last 10 days (2026-03-17 through 2026-03-27).\\n\\n2. Search each session for any instance when Tiny asked you to take notes, make a note, remember something, or similar di\nrective. Search for these patterns:\\n   - \\\"take notes\\\"\\n   - \\\"make a note\\\"\\n   - \\\"I want you to remember\\\"\\n   - \\\"note this\\\"\\n   - \\\"remember this\\\"\\n   - \\\"don't forget\\\"\\n   - Any explicit in\nstruction to save something to a file\\n\\n3. For each finding, record:\\n   - Date/time of the instruction\\n   - What Tiny asked you to note\\n   - Whether you actually noted it (yes/no/partial)\\n   - If\n yes: which file it was saved to\\n   - If no: why not (if discernible from context)\\n\\n4. Compile findings into a report at `memory/2026-03-27-note-compliance-audit.md` with:\\n   - Summary stats (tota\nl instructions found, total complied, total missed)\\n   - List of complied notes (with file locations)\\n   - List of missed notes (with what was asked)\\n   - Root cause analysis if patterns emerge\\n\\n\n5. ALSO: Using the same session files, find any feedback Tiny gave you that was NOT captured in any skills folder or memory file. This includes:\\n   - Corrections\\n   - Preferences stated\\n   - Style \ncritiques\\n   - Rules he gave you\\n\\n6. Save any uncaptured feedback to `memory/2026-03-27-uncaptured-feedback.md`\\n\\nDo NOT draft content. Do NOT do any Nava work. Only audit, record, and report.\\n\\n\nWhen done, output a one-line summary: \\\"AUDIT COMPLETE: X note instructions found, Y complied, Z missed. Report at memory/2026-03-27-note-compliance-audit.md\\\"\\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 1st, 202\n6 — 12:00 AM (Africa/Johannesburg) / 2026-03-31 22:00 UTC\"  }]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":22,"aggregated":"[  {    \"type\": \"text\",    \"text\": \"[cron:2ca3531d-d7c2-4846-b91f-804a1e726f81 Note-taking compliance audit (10-day session review)] ## Task: Note-taking compliance audit — 10-day session review\\n\\n\nYou are running an isolated audit. Your ONLY job:\\n\\n1. Using the session-logs skill (read ~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/session-logs/SKILL.md first, use jq commands), find ALL sessio\nn JSONL files modified in the last 10 days (2026-03-17 through 2026-03-27).\\n\\n2. Search each session for any instance when Tiny asked you to take notes, make a note, remember something, or similar di\nrective. Search for these patterns:\\n   - \\\"take notes\\\"\\n   - \\\"make a note\\\"\\n   - \\\"I want you to remember\\\"\\n   - \\\"note this\\\"\\n   - \\\"remember this\\\"\\n   - \\\"don't forget\\\"\\n   - Any explicit in\nstruction to save something to a file\\n\\n3. For each finding, record:\\n   - Date/time of the instruction\\n   - What Tiny asked you to note\\n   - Whether you actually noted it (yes/no/partial)\\n   - If\n yes: which file it was saved to\\n   - If no: why not (if discernible from context)\\n\\n4. Compile findings into a report at `memory/2026-03-27-note-compliance-audit.md` with:\\n   - Summary stats (tota\nl instructions found, total complied, total missed)\\n   - List of complied notes (with file locations)\\n   - List of missed notes (with what was asked)\\n   - Root cause analysis if patterns emerge\\n\\n\n5. ALSO: Using the same session files, find any feedback Tiny gave you that was NOT captured in any skills folder or memory file. This includes:\\n   - Corrections\\n   - Preferences stated\\n   - Style \ncritiques\\n   - Rules he gave you\\n\\n6. Save any uncaptured feedback to `memory/2026-03-27-uncaptured-feedback.md`\\n\\nDo NOT draft content. Do NOT do any Nava work. Only audit, record, and report.\\n\\n\nWhen done, output a one-line summary: \\\"AUDIT COMPLETE: X note instructions found, Y complied, Z missed. Report at memory/2026-03-27-note-compliance-audit.md\\\"\\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 1st, 202\n6 — 12:00 AM (Africa/Johannesburg) / 2026-03-31 22:00 UTC\"  }]","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775017914649}}
