apper\"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c4270028001=\"\" data-test-id=\"model-thoughts\" _nghost-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c524768972-64 ng-star-inserted\" style=\"height: auto;\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" xapautoid=\"\" class=\"model-thoughts ng-tns-c524768972-64\" id=\"xap-auto-id-11\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"thoughts-header ng-tns-c524768972-64\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" mat-button=\"\" data-test-id=\"thoughts-header-button\" class=\"mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c524768972-64 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed\" mat-ripple-loader-class-name=\"mat-mdc-button-ripple\" aria-controls=\"xap-auto-id-11\" aria-expanded=\"true\" jslog=\"247951;track:generic_click,impression\"><span class=\"mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple\"></span><span class=\"mdc-button__label\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"thoughts-header-button-content animated-text\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" role=\"status\" class=\"thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c524768972-64\"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c524768972-64 ng-star-inserted\">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c524768972-64\"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"expand_less\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c524768972-64 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"expand_less\" style=\"\"></mat-icon><!----><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class=\"mat-focus-indicator\"></span><span class=\"mat-mdc-button-touch-target\"></span><span class=\"mat-ripple mat-mdc-button-ripple\"></span></button></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" data-test-id=\"thoughts-content\" class=\"thoughts-content gds-italic ng-tns-c524768972-64 thoughts-content-expanded ng-trigger ng-trigger-thoughtsContentAnimation ng-star-inserted\" jslog=\"247952;track:impression,attention\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c524768972-64 ng-star-inserted\" style=\"\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"message-container ng-tns-c524768972-64\"><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c524768972-64 ng-animate-disabled\" _nghost-ng-c3044119038=\"\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3044119038=\"\" class=\"container\"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3044119038=\"\" _nghost-ng-c3255093193=\"\" id=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3255093193=\"\" inline-copy-host=\"\" class=\"markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color\" id=\"\" aria-live=\"off\" aria-busy=\"false\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;\"></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c524768972-64 ng-star-inserted\" style=\"\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"message-container ng-tns-c524768972-64\"><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c524768972=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c524768972-64 ng-animate-disabled\" _nghost-ng-c3044119038=\"\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3044119038=\"\" class=\"container\"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3044119038=\"\" _nghost-ng-c3255093193=\"\" id=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3255093193=\"\" inline-copy-host=\"\" class=\"markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color\" id=\"\" aria-live=\"off\" aria-busy=\"false\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;\"><p data-path-to-node=\"0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Analyzing the Article</b></p><p data-path-to-node=\"1\">I have started reviewing the article, carefully noting every element and referencing its source.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"2\"><b data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Refining the Approach</b></p><p data-path-to-node=\"3\">I'm adapting my approach to analyze changes effectively, considering contextual clues within multi-turn prompts.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"4\">I've already started to note how to balance empathy with candor, adapt tone, and avoid revealing instructions.\n270:I'm also paying attention to how to ask questions effectively.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Identifying Key Differences</b></p><p data-path-to-node=\"6\">I've pinpointed and cited several significant revisions, like the \"revolving door\" phrasing and meta title changes.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Pinpointing Revisions in Detail</b></p><p data-path-to-node=\"8\">I have located and meticulously cited more revisions, including section headings and title case usage.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><b data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Observing User's Adjustments</b></p><p data-path-to-node=\"10\">I've registered and cited the influx of second-person phrasing, now realizing it injects engaging conversational elements.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Detecting Question Omission</b></p><p data-path-to-node=\"12\">I've confirmed the user omitted the suggested engagement question within the conclusion.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><b data-path-to-node=\"13\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Tracking User Edits</b></p><p data-path-to-node=\"14\">I've documented the removal of \"11 PM\" and the \"owner and software\" phrase, and found new rhetorical questions.</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container></div></div><!----></div><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c4270028001=\"\" class=\"cdk-visually-hidden ng-star-inserted\"> The Content Architect said </h2><!----><!----><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c4270028001=\"\" class=\"model-response-text contains-extensions-response processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted has-thoughts\" _nghost-ng-c3044119038=\"\" style=\"height: auto;\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3044119038=\"\" class=\"container\"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c3044119038=\"\" _nghost-ng-c3255093193=\"\" id=\"message-content-id-r_7240695df028c656\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3255093193=\"\" inline-copy-host=\"\" class=\"markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color\" id=\"model-response-message-contentr_7240695df028c656\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-busy=\"false\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;\"><p data-path-to-node=\"0\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-19\"><span data-path-to-node=\"0,0\">I certainly noticed a few strategic shifts. It looks like you have struck a much better balance between high-authority \"forensic\" analysis and actual human readability. </span><span data-path-to-node=\"0,1\"><span class=\"citation-71\"></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"0,2\"><span class=\"citation-71\">The \"revolving door\" imagery is particularly sharp; it perfectly captures that feeling of a business spinning its wheels without gaining any real traction</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"0,3\"><span class=\"citation-71 citation-end-71\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"1\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"0,4\">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3999117843=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3999117843=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details. Opens side panel.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click,impression,attention\"><!----><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"link\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"link\"></mat-icon><!----></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p><p data-path-to-node=\"1\">Here are the specific changes I caught in this version of the <b data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-index-in-node=\"62\">Outsource Sales Rep</b> guide:</p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\">1. The \"Revolving Door\" Update</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"3\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-20\"><span data-path-to-node=\"3,0\"><span class=\"citation-70\"></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,1\"><span class=\"citation-70\">You successfully replaced the \"hiring stall\" jargon with a </span><b data-path-to-node=\"3,1\" data-index-in-node=\"59\"><span class=\"citation-70\">revolving door of hiring</span></b></span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,2\"><span class=\"citation-70 citation-end-70\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"2\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,3\">. </span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,4\"><span class=\"citation-69\"></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,5\"><span class=\"citation-69\">This is far more descriptive of the actual pain point: the endless cycle of hiring, training, and losing unmanaged freelancers</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,6\"><span class=\"citation-69 citation-end-69\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"3\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"3,7\">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3999117843=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3999117843=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details. Opens side panel.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click,impression,attention\"><!----><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"link\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"link\"></mat-icon><!----></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"4\">2. Rhetorical Engagement Hooks</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"5\">You have added conversational \"pattern interrupts\" at the beginning of several major sections:</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"6\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,0,0\"><span class=\"citation-68\"></span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"6,0,1\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-21\"><span data-path-to-node=\"6,0,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"6,0,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-68\">Section 4 (The Hunters-to-Clerks Drift):</span></b><span class=\"citation-68\"> \"How much time in a week is your sales team spending on their actual job, selling?\"</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,0,1,1\"><span class=\"citation-68 citation-end-68\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"4\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,0,1,2\">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3999117843=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3999117843=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details. Opens side panel.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click,impression,attention\"><!----><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"link\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"link\"></mat-icon><!----></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\"><span class=\"citation-67\"></span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,1\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-22\"><span data-path-to-node=\"6,1,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"6,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-67\">Section 5 (The Discovery Gap):</span></b><span class=\"citation-67\"> \"Are you confident that you know what the problems in your business actually are?\"</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,1,1,1\"><span class=\"citation-67 citation-end-67\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"5\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"5\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"5\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"5\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,1,1,2\">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3999117843=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3999117843=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details. Opens side panel.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click\"><!----><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" hide-from-message-actions=\"\" class=\"button-label gds-label-m hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"link\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"link\"></mat-icon>+3</span><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,2,0\"><span class=\"citation-66\"></span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-23\"><span data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-66\">Section 9 (Trust Signals):</span></b><span class=\"citation-66\"> \"Are your employees just mercenaries or dedicated followers to the cause?\"</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1,1\"><span class=\"citation-66 citation-end-66\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"6\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"6\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"6\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"6\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1,2\">.\n271:</span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1,3\"><span class=\"citation-65\"></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1,4\"><span class=\"citation-65\">These questions force the reader to stop and self-reflect before diving into the data</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1,5\"><span class=\"citation-65 citation-end-65\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"7\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"6,2,1,6\">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3999117843=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3999117843=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details. Opens side panel.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click\"><!----><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" hide-from-message-actions=\"\" class=\"button-label gds-label-m hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"link\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"link\"></mat-icon>+3</span><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node=\"7\">3. Second-Person Perspective</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"8\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-24\"><span data-path-to-node=\"8,0\"><span class=\"citation-64\"></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"8,1\"><span class=\"citation-64\">The second-person perspective (</span><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1\" data-index-in-node=\"31\"><span class=\"citation-64\">you/your</span></b><span class=\"citation-64\">) has made a calculated return in several places, particularly in those new rhetorical questions and the concluding sentences</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"8,2\"><span class=\"citation-64 citation-end-64\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"8\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"8\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"8\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c416062