"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"13\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"13\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"13\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"13\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"13\"><!----></sup></source-footnote><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"13\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,1,1,2\">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3999117843=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3999117843=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details. Opens side panel.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click\"><!----><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" hide-from-message-actions=\"\" class=\"button-label gds-label-m hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"link\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"link\"></mat-icon>+4</span><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,2,0\"><span class=\"citation-58\"></span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"12,2,1\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-28\"><span data-path-to-node=\"12,2,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,2,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-58\">Grammar Fix:</span></b><span class=\"citation-58\"> The paragraph regarding Customer Acquisition Costs (CAC) and the domestic labor market now flows logically while keeping the keyword and links intact</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,2,1,1\"><span class=\"citation-58 citation-end-58\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"14\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,2,1,2\">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3999117843=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3999117843=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details. Opens side panel.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click,impression,attention\"><!----><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"link\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"link\"></mat-icon><!----></button><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,3,0\"><span class=\"citation-57\"></span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-29\"><span data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-57\">Jargon Removal:</span></b><span class=\"citation-57\"> In the \"Building a Professional Department\" section, phrases like \"systemized firm\" have been replaced with \"Graduating from a manual hustle to a scalable venture\"</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1,1\"><span class=\"citation-57 citation-end-57\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"15\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1,2\">. </span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1,3\"><span class=\"citation-56\"></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1,4\"><span class=\"citation-56\">You also clarified the \"management layer\" as being in charge of \"hiring, training, and daily checks\" rather than just \"inserting a specialist between owner and software\"</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1,5\"><span class=\"citation-56 citation-end-56\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"16\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"12,3,1,6\">.</span><sources-carousel-inline ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c3999117843=\"\"><source-inline-chip _ngcontent-ng-c3999117843=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" class=\"source-inline-chip-container ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" cdkoverlayorigin=\"\" class=\"button multiple-button ng-star-inserted\" aria-label=\"View source details. Opens side panel.\" jslog=\"262206;track:generic_click\"><!----><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" hide-from-message-actions=\"\" class=\"button-label gds-label-m hide-from-message-actions ng-star-inserted\"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2182308453=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"link\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate symbol gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"link\"></mat-icon>+1</span><!----><!----><!----></button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></source-inline-chip><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></sources-carousel-inline></p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node=\"13\"><span class=\"citation-55\"></span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"14\" id=\"p-rc_571dee9f4614dd51-30\"><span data-path-to-node=\"14,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"14,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-55\">One quick observation:</span></b><span class=\"citation-55\"> I noticed the engagement question I suggested for the end of the conclusion (\"At what revenue milestone...\") was removed</span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"14,1\"><span class=\"citation-55 citation-end-55\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-source-index=\"17\"><!----></sup></source-footnote></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"14,2\">. </span><span data-path-to-node=\"14,3\"><span class=\"citation-54\"></span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"14,4\"><span class=\"citation-54\">Was that a deliberate choice to keep the ending more focused on the </span><b data-path-to-node=\"14,4\" data-index-in-node=\"68\"><span class=\"citation-54\">investor-grade stability</span></b><span class=\"citation-54\"> call to action? </span></span><span data-path-to-node=\"14,5\"><span class=\"citation-54 citation-end-54\"><source-footnote ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\" _nghost-ng-c4160627711=\"\"><sup _ngcontent-ng-c4160627711=\"\" class=\"superscript\" data-turn-