tect Custom Gem Show thinking Analyzing the Documents Okay, I'm diving into the materials now. I'm focusing on the Session Rules document, along with the various drafts and research material, to understand the context. My initial goal is to focus on critiquing drafts 3 and 4, keeping the new employee's actions in mind. I am developing an understanding of the relationship between all the s\n...","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775054321596}}
