{"type":"message","id":"21c27590","parentId":"694dea33","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:39:28.334Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_de8fb7d3-c7e1-41bf-863b-db55058be750","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Subagent Task]: You are a transcript mining agent. Read EVERY session file in the OpenClaw workspace and extract all meaningful content into permanent notes.\n\nWORKING DIRECTORY: /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace\n\nSESSION FILE LOCATIONS:\n- ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl\n- ~/.openclaw/agents/navaaa/sessions/*.jsonl\n- ~/TinyBackUp/*.jsonl\n- ~/.openclaw/workspace/TINYBU17Mar/*.jsonl\n- ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/transcript-mining/*.jsonl (if any)\n\nALREADY PROCESSED (do NOT re-read unless instructed):\n--\nSESSION FILES TO READ:\n1. ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/ — list all files, read any not listed above\n2. ~/.openclaw/agents/navaaa/sessions/ — list and read all\n3. ~/TinyBackUp/ — list and read any .jsonl files\n4. ~/.openclaw/workspace/TINYBU17Mar/ — read 7e318110 fully if not done\n5. ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/transcript-mining/ — check for any session files\n\nFOR EACH SESSION FILE YOU READ:\n1. Extract ALL user messages (role: user) — these are Tiny's words, highest priority\n2. Extract ALL assistant messages (role: assistant) — these are my responses\n3. Extract ANY decisions, rules, or agreements made in the conversation\n4. Extract ANY facts about Tiny, Nava, projects, preferences\n5. Extract ANY drafts, content, or substantive work products\n6. Extract ANY screenshots referenced (with paths if found)\n\nNOTES FILE: /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/transcript-mining/00_COMPREHENSIVE_READ.md\n\nIMPORTANT RULES:\n- After reading EACH session file, IMMEDIATELY append notes to the notes file before reading the next file\n- Never read an entire folder of sessions and THEN take notes — save notes after EACH file\n- Use python3 to parse JSONL: python3 -c \"import json; [print(json.dumps(js