{"type":"message","id":"4e38b8ee","parentId":"7c40d96b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:12:58.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_090d4258-441a-4f71-98ce-bcd648f8c31b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace && git commit -m \"Update editorial skills: add HumanizedGemini.html lessons, phase enforcement, keyword rules\n\nKey additions across all three skills (abroadworks-writing, nava-writing, editor):\n\n- Phase enforcement: no jumping H1→draft without H2/H3/Canvas approval\n- Comprehension vs vocabulary: unpack logic before synonym-swapping\n- Hallucination prevention: verify before referencing files/stats  \n- Paragraph independence: distinct beats not restatements\n- Transition discipline: Problem→Agitation→Solution, each earns its place\n- Suspend the win intro: acknowledge appeal then reveal failure\n- Edgy voice: every article needs its own edge\n- Keyword never bold: bold only in headings and callouts\n- Banned terms: trap, tax (structural), instruction tax/trap\n- Editorial housekeeping: meta info, callouts, FAQ integrity\n- AWAA prompt template updated with all new constraints\""}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":46821,"output":238,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47059,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775056378484}}
