hat I did.\n- Assistant: Best way to show you: give me the original AI version and your final version. I'll do a diff and tell you exactly what changed.\n\nFrom what I saw in the HumanizedGemini.html exchange, the key changes were:\n- Sentence-level rewrites (shorter, punchier)\n- Removing AI tell-tales (unnecessary caps, formulaic transitions)\n- \"Street-level\" word swaps (\"workforce\" → \"staff,\" etc.)\n\nBut I don't have the actual before/after files side by side. Where's the final version saved? Is it the `Updated: Outsource Sales Rep.md` file in your Downloads?","firstKeptEntryId":"88e5575c","tokensBefore":40082,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
