s\n- [ ] Extracting readable text from HumanizedGemini.html (blocked by large inline script data)\n- [ ] Final review of transitions after update\n- [ ] Adding AbroadWorks article link to introduction\n- [ ] Adding primary/secondary keywords to headings and body text\n\n### Blocked\n- Large inline script data in line 3 of HTML (546.9KB) is interfering with text extraction\n- Python extraction script was truncated at 15000 characters\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Python-based extraction approach**: Used HTMLParser with script/style removal to clean content before extracting text\n- **Differentiation strategy for Admin burden articles**: Using \"Identity Black Market\" and \"Administrative Amnesia\" pivots to avoid reprinting \"founders doing too much\" ar\n\n[Compaction summary truncated to fit budget]\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n- Compare early version documents (\"Final_ Outsource Sales Rep Guide.md\" and \"Outsource Sales Rep Guide.md\") with the final draft (\"Updated_ Outsource Sales Rep.md\") to identify any differences or notable issues.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Files are located in /mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/\n- Focus on .md (markdown) file comparisons\n- .odt files also exist in the same directory\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Listed files in Downloads folder matching \"outsource\" pattern\n- [x] Read three .md files: \"Outsource Sales Rep Guide.md\", \"Final_ Outsource Sales Rep Guide.md\", and \"Updated_ Outsource Sales Rep.md\"\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Comparison analysis between versions not yet provided to user\n\n### Blocked\n- None\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Read markdown versions first**: Assistant chose to read the .md files before the larger .odt files for initial comparison\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Provide detailed comparison of the three documents identifying differences in content, meta information, and structure\n2. Highlight any discrepancies or issues found between early and final versions\n3. If needed, compare .odt