{"type":"message","id":"aeef376b","parentId":"0ea51db8","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:39:27.424Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_60170c50-7f68-45eb-87e2-aa33906cc641","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# X029 — \"EB-3 or TN: The Wrong Question\"\n\n## The Post\n\nEB-3 or TN?\n\nThat's the wrong question.\n\nThe EB-3 pathway is permanent residency. Slower, costlier upfront. The nurse arrives as a green card holder.\n\nThe TN pathway is temporary work authorization. Faster, cheaper. Restricted to Canadian and Mexican nationals under USMCA.\n\nThese are not two options on the same menu. They answer different strategic questions.\n\nThe facilities getting this right are running both.\n\nOne pipeline for positions to fill in the next six months. One pipeline for the permanent staffing base built over three years.\n\nSeparate populations. Different timelines. One staffing plan.\n\nRun it to three years and the numbers tell a different story.\n\nNava Healthcare runs both tracks.\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n- Platform: Nava Healthcare X (@NavaHealthcare)\n- Character count: ~890 (under 1000 ✅)\n- CTA: Nava Healthcare website / contact\n- Theme: parallel track strategy, anti-binary framing"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"# X029 — \"EB-3 or TN: The Wrong Question\"\n\n## The Post\n\nEB-3 or TN?\n\nThat's the wrong question.\n\nThe EB-3 pathway is permanent residency. Slower, costlier upfront. The nurse arrives as a green card holder.\n\nThe TN pathway is temporary work authorization. Faster, cheaper. Restricted to Canadian and Mexican nationals under USMCA.\n\nThese are not two options on the same menu. They answer different strategic questions.\n\nThe facilities getting this right are running both.\n\nOne pipeline for positions to fill in the next six months. One pipeline for the permanent staffing base built over three years.\n\nSeparate populations. Different timelines. One staffing plan.\n\nRun it to three years and the numbers tell a different story.\n\nNava Healthcare runs both tracks.\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n- Platform: Nava Healthcare X (@NavaHealthcare)\n- Character count: ~890 (under 1000 ✅)\n- CTA: Nava Healthcare website / contact\n- Theme: parallel track strategy, anti-binary framing","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775057967418}}
{"type":"message","id":"c340523f","parentId":"aeef376b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:39:45.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes, I can see the queue from the Mar 28 session. Here's what's in drafts:\n\n| File | Topic | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| `li026_linkedin.md` | EB-3 vs TN parallel track | ✅ Final — needs review |\n| `x029_eb3_vs_tn.md` | X version of above | ✅ Ready |\n| `li026_v2.md` | Blog post (15KB) — foundation for LI026 | ✅ Exists |\n| `li027_nursesphere_introduction.md` | NurseSphere intro | Draft |\n| `li028_13_week_problem.md` | 13-week problem | Draft |\n| `li029_eb3_vs_tn.md` | EB-3 vs TN (detailed) | Draft |\n| `li030_parallel_track.md` | Parallel track strategy | Draft |\n| `li031_nursesphere_recruitment.md` | NurseSphere recruitment | Draft |\n\nBefore we queue 6 posts — you mentioned wanting to launch the **new blog post** and build on it. Question: is the blog post still `li026_v2.md` (the Mar 28 foundation)? And the plan is:\n1. Finalize blog post → 2. Derive LI026 from it → 3. Derive X029?\n\nOr are these 5-6 drafts already separate topics we should treat as independent LinkedIn posts?\n\nAlso: do you want to post LI026 (EB-3/TN) today? It's fully drafted and strong."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":26530,"output":587,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775057985714}}
{"type":"message","id":"6aa041f1","parentId":"c340523f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:43:06.310Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-01 17:43 GMT+2] I have posted a new blog post, check the live Nava blog. \n\nCritical question: There is a post on LinkedIn, it starts with this:\nIn long-term care, the patient at the end of the hall has been disoriented three times this year.\n\nThe same routine. A different face. A different name.\n\nDid you post this?? I don't remember doing this."}],"timestamp":1775058186302}}
