{"type":"message","id":"83354fda","parentId":"695012f7","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:53:11.302Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_0a14d6a4-1dc4-4abd-a6df-f902b5ef4eb8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"s=\"cdk-visually-hidden\"> You said </span><p _ngcontent-ng-c1962246251=\"\" class=\"query-text-line ng-star-inserted\"> Ok, this is a good start but how certain are you that Nava handles cohorts of up to 100 nurses, etc. This prompt should also include research into NurseSphere by Nava, no? I want to make sure we are not making claims that are not real. <!----><!----></p><!----></div><!----><!----><!----></span></span><!----></div><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></user-query-content></span></user-query><!----><!----><model-response _ngcontent-ng-c2346523679=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\"><response-container _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" _nghost-ng-c623431008=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c623431008-183 reduced-bottom-padding ng-star-inserted\" jslog=\"188576;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_53e748c9e2042c18&quot;,&quot;c_106573abd16b5e1f&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,0]];mutable:true\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c623431008=\"\" class=\"response-container response-container-with-gpi ng-tns-c623431008-183 no-background\" jslog=\"173900;track:impression,attention\"><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c623431008=\"\" class=\"response-container-header ng-tns-c623431008-183 ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c623431008=\"\" class=\"response-container-header-controls ng-tns-c623431008-183\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c623431008=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c623431008-183 tts ng-trigger ng-trigger-singleResponseEnter ng-star-inserted\" style=\"\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c623431008=\"\" class=\"single-draft-response-container ng-tns-c623431008-183\"><!----></div></div><!----><tts-control _ngcontent-ng-c623431008=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2487165891=\"\" class=\"ng-tn