=\"\" data-test-id=\"user-notice\" _nghost-ng-c1303319782=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c623431008-188 ng-star-inserted\" style=\"\"><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1303319782=\"\" class=\"safety-disclaimer-container-for-medical ng-star-inserted\" jslog=\"241129;track:impression\"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1303319782=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"error\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate icon gds-icon-l google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"error\"></mat-icon><div _ngcontent-ng-c1303319782=\"\" data-test-id=\"notice-text\" class=\"gds-body-m notice-text\"> This is for informational purposes only. For medical advice or diagnosis, consult a professional. </div></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></user-notice><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"response-content ng-tns-c623431008-188\"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"thoughts-container ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"thoughts-content ng-star-inserted\" style=\"\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"thoughts-wrapper\"><!----><model-thoughts _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" data-test-id=\"model-thoughts\" _nghost-ng-c1490714386=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c1490714386-190 ng-star-inserted\" style=\"height: auto;\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1490714386=\"\" xapautoid=\"\" class=\"model-thoughts ng-tns-c1490714386-190\" id=\"xap-auto-id-8\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1490714386=\"\" class=\"thoughts-header ng-tns-c1490714386-190\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1490714386=\"\" mat-button=\"\" data-test-id=\"thoughts-header-button\" class=\"mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base thoughts-header-button ng-tns-c1490714386-190 mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed\" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized=\"\" mat-ripple-loader-class-name=\"mat-mdc-button-ripple\" aria-controls=\"xap-auto-id-8\" aria-expanded=\"false\" jslog=\"247951;track:generic_click,impression\"><span class=\"mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple\"></span><span class=\"mdc-button__label\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1490714386=\"\" class=\"thoughts-header-button-content animated-text\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1490714386=\"\" role=\"status\" class=\"thoughts-header-button-label ng-tns-c1490714386-190\"><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c1490714386=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c1490714386-190 ng-star-inserted\">Show thinking</span><!----></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1490714386=\"\" class=\"thoughts-header-button-icons ng-tns-c1490714386-190\"><!----><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1490714386=\"\" role=\"img\" fonticon=\"expand_more\" class=\"mat-icon notranslate thoughts-header-button-icon ng-tns-c1490714386-190 google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-mat-icon-type=\"font\" data-mat-icon-name=\"expand_more\"></mat-icon><!----></div></div></span><!----><span class=\"mat-focus-indicator\"></span><span class=\"mat-mdc-button-touch-target\"></span></button></div><!----><!----></div></model-thoughts><!----></div><!----></div><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"cdk-visually-hidden ng-star-inserted\"> Article Architect said </h2><!----><!----><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"model-response-text processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted has-thoughts\" _nghost-ng-c1591561687=\"\" style=\"height: auto;\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1591561687=\"\" class=\"container\"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c1591561687=\"\" _nghost-ng-c25865369=\"\" id=\"message-content-id-r_bef73cbc2027e669\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c25865369=\"\" inline-copy-host=\"\" class=\"markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color\" id=\"model-response-message-contentr_bef73cbc2027e669\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-busy=\"false\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;\"><p data-path-to-node=\"0\">You are absolutely right to be cautious. According to the <b data-path-to-node=\"0\" data-index-in-node=\"58\">Content Bible Protocol</b>, we must never make a claim we cannot back up with a \"Source of Truth\" (SoT).</p><p data-path-to-node=\"1\">I have cross-referenced your website’s operational pages to verify the specific details of the NurseSphere™ program. Here is what is confirmed:</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"2\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">The 100-Nurse Cohort:</b> This is a verified Nava capability. The program has successfully processed groups of nearly <b data-path-to-node=\"2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"114\">100 registered nurses and physical therapists at once</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"2,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"2,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">The 3-Year / 6,000-Hour Commitment:</b> This is the contractual anchor of every placement.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Green Card Status:</b> Candidates arrive as permanent residents (<b data-path-to-node=\"2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"61\">EB-3 visa</b>), not on temporary work permits.</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node=\"3\">However, to make the <b data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"21\">Research Prompt</b> truly \"deep\" and \"neutral\" (and to ensure we aren't just echoing our own marketing), we should look for industry data that validates <i data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"170\">why</i> these specific features (EB-3, 3-year terms, cohorts) are superior to the alternatives.</p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"4\">REFINED DEEP RESEARCH PROMPT (v2.0)</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><i data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Please run this in an external tool like Perplexity or Google for your SoT:</i></p><blockquote data-path-to-node=\"6\"><p data-path-to-node=\"6,0\">\"Research the operational impact of international nurse recruitment programs that utilize the <b data-path-to-node=\"6,0\" data-index-in-node=\"94\">EB-3 Immigrant Visa (Green Card)</b> pathway compared to temporary visa pathways (H-1B, J-1) in the U.S.</p><ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"6,1\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0,0\">Find data on <b data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"13\">retention rates</b> for nurses on a 3-year (6,000-hour) commitment versus the turnover rates of 13-week travel nurse contracts.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,1,0\">Investigate the success of <b data-path-to-node=\"6,1,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"27\">'hiring cohorts'</b> (groups of 50-100+) in solving systemic staffing shortages in rural vs. urban health systems.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,2,0\">Look for studies or financial models comparing the <b data-path-to-node=\"6,1,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"51\">all-in cost</b> of an international placement (including legal/relocation) versus the long-term cost of agency labor.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,3,0\">Search for mentions of <b data-path-to-node=\"6,1,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"23\">'NurseSphere' by Nava Healthcare</b> to see how it is positioned in the market relative to other international recruitment firms like Health Carousel or O'Grady Peyton.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,4,0\">Find evidence regarding the impact of <b data-path-to-node=\"6,1,4,0\" data-index-in-node=\"38\">'pay parity'</b> (aligning international nurse pay with local staff) on long-term retention and team morale.\"</p></li></ol></blockquote><h3 data-path-to-node=\"7\">Why this is better:</h3><ul data-path-to-node=\"8\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Validation:</b> By including \"NurseSphere,\" the search tool will find our existing documentation and compare it against industry standards.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Neutrality:</b> We aren't asking \"Why is NurseSphere better?\" We are asking for the \"operational impact\" and \"comparative ROI,\" which will give us the hard numbers we need for a 1,800-word deep dive.</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><b data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Next Step:</b> Once you have the results from this search, please paste them here. I will then perform <b data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"99\">Protocol 7.1 (SoT Ingestion)</b> and generate the <b data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"145\">Skeleton Outline</b>.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"10\">Do you want to add anything else to this prompt before you run it?</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"response-footer gap has-thoughts complete\"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" class=\"sources-list ng-star-inserted\"><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" _nghost-ng-c2352021945=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\" style=\"\"><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c623431008=\"\" class=\"response-container-footer ng-tns-c623431008-188 ng-star-inserted\"><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c2252882863=\"\" footer=\"\" _nghost-ng-c3718689617=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c3718689617-191 ng-star-inserted\" style=\"\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3718689617=\"\" class=\"actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c3718689617-191\"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3718689617=\"\" class=\"buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c3718689617-191 ng-star-inserted\"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c3718689617=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1411699388=\"\" class=\"ng-tns-c3718689617-191 ng-star-inserted\"><button _ngcontent-ng-c1411699388=\"\" mat-icon-button=\"\" mattooltip=\"Good response\" aria-label=\"Good resp