{"type":"message","id":"86314c0f","parentId":"811a7d11","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:03:22.316Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now TinyQE pass 1:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_2ecade4c-013d-4b58-b0a0-d7bae4de92dd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/tinyqe && python3 tinyqe.py \"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/rag/drafts/visa_pathway/v3_merged.md\" 2>&1"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":43159,"output":93,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43252,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775059402315}}
{"type":"message","id":"e926ff1b","parentId":"86314c0f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:03:23.659Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_2ecade4c-013d-4b58-b0a0-d7bae4de92dd","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"TinyQE Assessment — Generic\n\nOverall: Needs Work. Content shows promise but requires significant improvement.\n\nTop 3 Priorities:\n1. Linguistic Integrity (severity: high | weight: 8%) — 2 mechanical errors detected. Highest priority: missing space after period\n   → Address errors in order: missing space after period, missing space after period\n2. Thesis Clarity (severity: high | weight: 8%) — No clear thesis detected.\n   → State your central claim clearly in the opening paragraph.\n3. Structural Completeness (severity: high | weight: 8%) — Structure is incomplete. Missing: CLAIM, EVIDENCE, RESOLUTION.\n   → Restructure to include: claim → setup → evidence → complication → resolution.\n\nNote: Scores are diagnostic, not judgmental. Focus on the priority queue for actionable feedback.\nFormat detected: Generic (confidence: 50%)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1332,"aggregated":"TinyQE Assessment — Generic\n\nOverall: Needs Work. Content shows promise but requires significant improvement.\n\nTop 3 Priorities:\n1. Linguistic Integrity (severity: high | weight: 8%) — 2 mechanical errors detected. Highest priority: missing space after period\n   → Address errors in order: missing space after period, missing space after period\n2. Thesis Clarity (severity: high | weight: 8%) — No clear thesis detected.\n   → State your central claim clearly in the opening paragraph.\n3. Structural Completeness (severity: high | weight: 8%) — Structure is incomplete. Missing: CLAIM, EVIDENCE, RESOLUTION.\n   → Restructure to include: claim → setup → evidence → complication → resolution.\n\nNote: Scores are diagnostic, not judgmental. Focus on the priority queue for actionable feedback.\nFormat detected: Generic (confidence: 50%)","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775059403655}}
{"type":"message","id":"90d569ec","parentId":"e926ff1b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:03:32.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"TinyQE keeps defaulting to Generic instead of blog format. Let me check the CLI options:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_119b68f9-050c-4596-94c0-2b99043e4e80","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/tinyqe && python3 tinyqe.py --help 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":43438,"output":258,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43696,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775059412436}}
{"type":"message","id":"9cc894b1","parentId":"90d569ec","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:03:32.508Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_119b68f9-050c-4596-94c0-2b99043e4e80","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"usage: tinyqe.py [-h] [--format {json,narrative}]\n                 [--dimensions DIMENSIONS [DIMENSIONS ...]]\n                 [text]\n\nTinyQE: Tiny Quality Evaluator\n\npositional arguments:\n  text                  Text to evaluate. If not provided, reads from stdin.\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  --format {json,narrative}\n                        Output format\n  --dimensions DIMENSIONS [DIMENSIONS ...]\n                        Specific dimensions to run (e.g., A1 A2 B1). Default:\n                        all available."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":53,"aggregated":"usage: tinyqe.py [-h] [--format {json,narrative}]\n                 [--dimensions DIMENSIONS [DIMENSIONS ...]]\n                 [text]\n\nTinyQE: Tiny Quality Evaluator\n\npositional arguments:\n  text                  Text to evaluate. If not provided, reads from stdin.\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  --format {json,narrative}\n                        Output format\n  --dimensions DIMENSIONS [DIMENSIONS ...]\n                        Specific dimensions to run (e.g., A1 A2 B1). Default:\n                        all available.","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775059412500}}
