{"type":"message","id":"36d96695","parentId":"9f9d7920","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:06:40.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The \"missing space after period\" detections are all false positives — the regex `[^\\s]\\.[^\\s]` catches periods before newlines, blockquotes, and asterisks. TinyQE has a bug in its linguistic integrity analyzer. The only genuine mechanical error in V3 is the URL: `navahc.com/eb3.tn` → should be `eb-3.tn`. Let me fix that:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_ec1001cf-df60-44fe-9764-0e897fb251d9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"eb3.tn\\|eb-3.tn\" /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/rag/drafts/visa_pathway/v3_merged.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":45231,"output":1387,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775059600544}}
