{"type":"message","id":"5714d810","parentId":"808ba73b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:36:05.088Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_1f9370de-c1f0-45ef-b938-169dde1495a3","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"TinyQE Assessment — Generic\n\nOverall: Actionable. Content has strengths but needs refinement in key areas.\n\nTop 3 Priorities:\n1. Structural Completeness (severity: high | weight: 8%) — Structure is incomplete. Missing: CLAIM, EVIDENCE, RESOLUTION.\n   → Restructure to include: claim → setup → evidence → complication → resolution.\n2. Evidence Quality (severity: high | weight: 8%) — Claims lack evidential support.\n   → Your claims need data, statistics, expert opinions, or clear examples to be credible.\n3. Argumentative Rigor (severity: high | weight: 8%) — Lacks clear argument structure (claim, evidence, reasoning).\n   → Restructure to include: clear claim → supporting evidence → logical reasoning (because, therefore, etc.).\n\nNote: Scores are diagnostic, not judgmental. Focus on the priority queue for actionable feedback.\nFormat detected: Generic (confidence: 50%)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1453,"aggregated":"TinyQE Assessment — Generic\n\nOverall: Actionable. Content has strengths but needs refinement in key areas.\n\nTop 3 Priorities:\n1. Structural Completeness (severity: high | weight: 8%) — Structure is incomplete. Missing: CLAIM, EVIDENCE, RESOLUTION.\n   → Restructure to include: claim → setup → evidence → complication → resolution.\n2. Evidence Quality (severity: high | weight: 8%) — Claims lack evidential support.\n   → Your claims need data, statistics, expert opinions, or clear examples to be credible.\n3. Argumentative Rigor (severity: high | weight: 8%) — Lacks clear argument structure (claim, evidence, reasoning).\n   → Restructure to include: clear claim → supporting evidence → logical reasoning (because, therefore, etc.).\n\nNote: Scores are diagnostic, not judgmental.