{"type":"message","id":"86a707ea","parentId":"5714d810","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:36:09.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. The Linguistic Integrity priority is gone — confirming both fixes worked:\n1. ✅ 3-sentence paragraph fixed (merged into 4-sentence with added clause)\n2. ✅ Bold-in-body violations fixed (removed all subsection bold labels)\n\nThe remaining feedback is now substantive and actionable — structural completeness, evidence quality, and argumentative rigor. These are the kinds of notes an editor would give on a draft, not mechanical errors.\n\nLet me commit the changes and then we can move forward:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_fe426d91-998e-4f54-8b9f-1dd76020ab09","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace && git add /mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/Visa\\ Pathway\\ Comparison\\ v3.md && git commit -m \"Editor skill compliance: fixed 3-sentence paragraph and bold-in-body violations in Visa Pathway v3\""}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"nemotron-3-super:cloud","usage":{"input":59269,"output":198,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59467,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775061369974}}
