{"type":"message","id":"a97173b9","parentId":"56b54af3","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:52:08.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I don't see a specific timeline range mentioned in the current version. Let me check if I need to add the 12-48 month range explicitly. Looking back at the feedback, the error was citing \"16 to 54 months\" when the SoT says \"12 to 48 months\". Since I don't see a specific range in v4, I should check if it's implied correctly or if I need to make it explicit.\n\nActually, looking at the text: \"Facilities requiring positions filled within six months cannot rely on EB-3 due to its minimum three-year timeline before investment math works\" — this is correct (3 years = 36 months, which falls within the 12-48 month range). I don't need to specify the exact range unless it's being cited as a specific number.\n\nLet me check for premium processing:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_132361d9-a6a0-4a8c-9d5c-a05231fe951b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -i \"premium.*process\\|15.*business\\|45.*calendar\" /mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/Visa\\ Pathway\\ Comparison\\ v4_SOP_Compliant.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"nemotron-3-super:cloud","usage":{"input":72153,"output":252,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72405,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775062328208}}
{"type":"message","id":"729a0a87","parentId":"a97173b9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:52:08.237Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_132361d9-a6a0-4a8c-9d5c-a05231fe951b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. Premium processing under Form I-907 offers 15 business day adjudication for eligible filings at $2,965 per filing.\nFurthermore, the State Department visa bulletin for April 2026 demonstrates material improvements in EB-3 processing for Rest of World candidates, with the designation moved to \"Dates for Filing = Current\" enabling immediate foreign labor certification filings against the current fiscal year. Furthermore, premium processing under Form I-907 remains available at $2,965 per filing, providing 15 business day adjudication for eligible underlying filings as confirmed by the March 2026 update to official processing time guidelines."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":13,"aggregated":"4. Premium processing under Form I-907 offers 15 business day adjudication for eligible filings at $2,965 per filing.\nFurthermore, the State Department visa bulletin for April 2026 demonstrates material improvements in EB-3 processing for Rest of World candidates, with the designation moved to \"Dates for Filing = Current\" enabling immediate foreign labor certification filings against the current fiscal year. Furthermore, premium processing under Form I-907 remains available at $2,965 per filing, providing 15 business day adjudication for eligible underlying filings as confirmed by the March 2026 update to official processing time guidelines.","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775062328231}}
{"type":"message","id":"cbba6b76","parentId":"729a0a87","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:52:17.221Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect — I have \"15 business day adjudication\" correctly, and no mention of \"45 calendar days\".\n\nNow let me do a final check on the transitions to make sure I'm not overusing \"Furthermore\":"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_1b255c50-bb79-4c5b-99a6-cb03913381ad","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -o \"Furthermore\" /mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/Visa\\ Pathway\\ Comparison\\ v4_SOP_Compliant.md | wc -l"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"nemotron-3-super:cloud","usage":{"input":72562,"output":107,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72669,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775062337217}}
