{"type":"message","id":"bce29f62","parentId":"04a3cffa","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:54:00.766Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I think I'm misunderstanding something fundamental. Let me re-read the feedback very carefully:\n\n> * **The 3x3 Symmetry Rule:** You currently have **four** H2 sections. To comply, we must consolidate this into exactly **three** H2s, each with **three** H3 subsections.\n\nAnd looking at the current v3 that they were assessing:\n- It had 4 H2 sections (You're Asking the Wrong Question, The Math You've Never Seen Laid Out, 2026 Forecast..., The Right Answer Depends...)\n- It had ZERO H3 sections\n\nSo to fix it, I need:\n- Exactly 3 H2 sections (down from 4)\n- Each H2 section must have exactly 3 H3 subsections (up from 0)\n\nThis means I need 9 total H3 sections (3 × 3).\n\nLet me check what I currently have in v4:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_611d2c72-7701-4582-ab70-1f9b7ad770ec","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"^## \" /mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/Visa\\ Pathway\\ Comparison\\ v4_SOP_Compliant.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"nemotron-3-super:cloud","usage":{"input":74566,"output":254,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775062440762}}
