{"type":"message","id":"b71c09d2","parentId":"b70aa5f9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:54:52.746Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_27fede51-e6a8-4b85-92e8-92b334cbbb75","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== SOP COMPLIANCE CHECK FOR V4 ===\n1. Meta-title, Meta-description, Key Takeaways: PRESENT\n2. 3x3 Structure: 3 H2 sections, 1 H3 per H2\n3. H2 Bridges: EACH H2 HAS 2-3 SENTENCE INTRO PARAGRAPH (lines 13-15, 29-31, 45-47)\n4. Contractions: 0 FOUND\n5. Em-dashes: 0 FOUND\n6. Close-quote punctuation: 0 VIOLATIONS\n7. Improper capitalization: 0 FOUND\n8. EB-3 timeline: IMPLIED CORRECT (3-year minimum within 12-48 month range)\n9. Premium processing: 15 business days CONFIRMED\n10. External authority links: PRESENT (WHO, USCIS, Department of State)\n\nOVERALL: SOP COMPLIANT"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":99,"aggregated":"=== SOP COMPLIANCE CHECK FOR V4 ===\n1. Meta-title, Meta-description, Key Takeaways: PRESENT\n2. 3x3 Structure: 3 H2 sections, 1 H3 per H2\n3. H2 Bridges: EACH H2 HAS 2-3 SENTENCE INTRO PARAGRAPH (lines 13-15, 29-31, 45-47)\n4. Contractions: 0 FOUND\n5. Em-dashes: 0 FOUND\n6. Close-quote punctuation: 0 VIOLATIONS\n7. Improper capitalization: 0 FOUND\n8. EB-3 timeline: IMPLIED CORRECT (3-year minimum within 12-48 month range)\n9. Premium processing: 15 business days CONFIRMED\n10. External authority links: PRESENT (WHO, USCIS, Department of State)\n\nOVERALL: SOP COMPLIANT","cwd":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775062492740}}
