{"type":"message","id":"9154bcea","parentId":"8ee7b86b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:01:11.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_1b147557-1334-4628-ab43-fa4a1723b2f1","name":"edit","arguments":{"new_string":"### Hallucination Prevention\nNever hallucinate file names, article titles, or stats. Always verify against actual files and documents before referencing. CustomGPT invented \"The Upwork Trap\" and \"The Fiverr Illusion\" — articles that don't exist on AbroadWorks.\n\n### Factual Accuracy (Critical — immigration content especially)\nImmigration facts are verifiable and readers WILL catch errors. Before publishing:\n- **EB-3 processing times**: Verify current DoS and USCIS published times. Do not use outdated figures. Premium processing for EB-3 I-485 is 15 business days (FY2026), not 45 calendar days.\n- **Visa bulletin designations**: Confirm \"Dates for Filing\" vs \"Final Action Date\" behavior per current bulletin.\n- **Numbers in quotes**: Spell out numbers in text when used as proper nouns (write \"EB-3\" not \"EB3\" or \"eb-3\").\n- **Fee structures**: Verify all-in costs against current USCIS/NVC fee schedules.\n- **When in doubt**: Flag uncertain claims to the user rather than publishing unverified facts.","old_string":"### Hallucination Prevention\nNever hallucinate file names, article titles, or stats. Always verify against actual files and documents before referencing. CustomGPT invented \"The Upwork Trap\" and \"The Fiverr Illusion\" — articles that don't exist on AbroadWorks.","path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/editor/SKILL.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":26984,"output":354,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27338,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775062871885}}
