{"type":"message","id":"91b850ad","parentId":"16a1ae34","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:02:03.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Skill updated with 5 key additions from the Custom GPT feedback session:\n\n1. **No contractions in formal content** — LinkedIn/X can use them, articles cannot\n2. **No close-quote punctuation violations** — period goes outside the quote when the quote is a fragment, not a full sentence\n3. **Factual accuracy rules for immigration content** — processing times, visa bulletin designations, fee structures — verify before publishing\n4. **2x4-6 rule scoped** — applies to blog articles only, not LinkedIn/X/SoT formats\n5. **Never write exactly 3 sentences** — called out explicitly as the most common AI drafting pattern\n\nAlso added a new section: *\"Custom GPT Feedback — What It Catches\"* — so we know what to self-edit before sending anything to Custom GPT.\n\nWhile you wait for their review, I'll also flag the current Visa Pathway v4 for any issues I can already see. Back in a bit."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":28828,"output":212,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29040,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775062923315}}
