{"type":"message","id":"58692ca4","parentId":"80dc4be7","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:27:33.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me update memory:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_e478e825-04df-4880-abb1-ab0ab53fa0d8","name":"edit","arguments":{"new_string":"**Files modified:**\n- `/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/editor/SKILL.md` — updated and committed\n- `/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/Visa Pathway Comparison v4_Nava_Focused.md` — created earlier\n\n**Apr 1, 19:08 UTC — Custom GPT v4 critique + v5 created:**\n- Second Custom GPT critique found additional issues: missing meta-description, Key Takeaways block (Nava blog format confirmed via navahc.com), \"Furthermore\" crutch throughout, EB-3 timeline still wrong (16-54 vs correct 12-48 per SoT), premium processing \"45 calendar days\" (should be 15 business days), capitalized operational terms\n- Created `Visa Pathway Comparison v5.md` in Downloads — all fixes applied\n- Key Takeaways block added (5 items, per Nava blog format)\n- Meta-title and meta-description added (CMS scaffolding, stripped at publish)\n- All 4 \"Furthermore\" transitions replaced with diagnostic/additive alternatives\n- EB-3 timeline corrected to \"12 to 48 months\" throughout\n- Premium processing corrected to \"15 business days\" throughout\n- Sources section added at bottom with raw URLs (DoS Visa Bulletin, USCIS, HWRA)\n- Operational terms (critical mass, job embeddedness) left lowercase (were already lowercase in v4)\n- Editor skill fully updated with Nava blog requirements section\n- Skill committed to git\n\n**TrnsBank:** Still under 200 messages. Awaiting Tiny's lock signal.\n\n**Outstanding (unchanged):**\n- Nava RAG full build — deferred, awaiting Tiny direction\n- VPS research — Hetzner vs CloudAfrica, deferred\n- TinyQE Phase 2/3 — pending\n- 5 no-bylines blog articles — pending Tiny review\n- LI26/X18 rebuild — pending decision (article published April 1)\n- GitHub remote for Restore Kit — not set up","old_string":"**Files modified:**\n- `/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/skills/editor/SKILL.md` — updated and committed\n- `/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/Visa Pathway Comparison v4_Nava_Focused.md` — created\n\n**TinyQE remaining issues (post-v4 fixes):**\n- Structural Completeness: Missing CLAIM, EVIDENCE, RESOLUTION structure\n- Evidence Quality: Claims lack evidential support\n- Argumentative Rigor: Lacks clear argument structure\n\n**These are substantive editorial notes** — not mechanical errors. TinyQE linguistic_integrity analyzer now passing (all bold/contraction/em-dash violations resolved).\n\n**TrnsBank:** Still under 200 messages. Awaiting Tiny's lock signal.\n\n**Outstanding (unchanged):**\n- Nava RAG full build — deferred, awaiting Tiny direction\n- VPS research — Hetzner vs CloudAfrica, deferred\n- TinyQE Phase 2/3 — pending\n- 5 no-bylines blog articles — pending Tiny review\n- LI26/X18 rebuild — pending decision (article published April 1)\n- GitHub remote for Restore Kit — not set up","path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-01.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":46311,"output":748,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47059,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775064453569}}
