{"type":"message","id":"ce72f54d","parentId":"6cf5c89a","timestamp":"2026-04-02T00:03:27.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_f4a4bea2-9bc9-45c4-87d0-3b65dbc9914e","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/OneDrive/Apps/Dawn-Restore/20260402/RESTORE_INSTRUCTIONS.md","content":"# Dawn Restore Instructions\n\n**Last updated:** 2026-04-02  \n**Purpose:** Rebuild everything on a fresh-out-of-the-box computer from scratch.\n\n---\n\n## What's Included\n\n- `memory/` — Daily memory files (continuity + learned rules)\n- `workspace/` — Full OpenClaw workspace (skills, agents, tools, configs)\n- `openclaw.json` — Gateway config (tokens, channels, cron jobs)\n- `RESTORE_INSTRUCTIONS.md` — This file\n- `GIT_REPO.md` — Git remote setup instructions\n\n---\n\n## Step 1 — Install OpenClaw\n\nOn a fresh Windows machine:\n\n```powershell\nnpm install -g openclaw\n```\n\nOr via OpenClaw installer if available.\n\n---\n\n## Step 2 — Replicate WSL2 + Ollama Environment\n\nThis workspace assumes:\n- **WSL2** (Windows Subsystem for Linux 2)\n- **Ollama** running on Windows host at `localhost:11434`\n\nIf you need to set up Ollama on Windows:\n1. Download from https://ollama.com\n2. Install and pull models: `ollama pull minimax-m2.7`, `ollama pull gemma3:27b`\n\n---\n\n## Step 3 — Restore Your Workspace\n\n**Option A — From Git (recommended)**\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/dawn-workspace.git ~/.openclaw/workspace\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\ngit pull origin main\n```\n\n**Option B — From Restore Kit**\n\n```bash\n# Extract zip to ~/.openclaw/workspace\n# Then restore memory + config\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 4 — Restore Config\n\n```bash\ncp openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 5 — Re-authenticate\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway start\n# Then re-link WhatsApp via QR code\n```\n\n---\n\n## Step 6 — Verify Everything\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n---\n\n## What's NOT in This Kit\n\n- `agents/main/sessions/` — Session logs (large, personal, not needed for restore)\n- `browser_profiles/` — Browser automation profiles\n- `.git/` — Workspace git history\n- `node_modules/` — Installed packages (rebuilt via npm install)\n\n---\n\n## Key Files to Know\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `memory/MEMORY.md` | Long-term memory + identity |\n| `SOUL.md` | Who Dawn is |\n| `AGENTS.md` | Operating rules |\n| `skills/editor/SKILL.md` | Writing + editorial standards |\n| `TOOLS.md` | Environment-specific config |\n\n---\n\n## Workspace Git Remote\n\nThe workspace has a git remote. Set it up:\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\ngit remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/dawn-workspace.git\ngit push -u origin main\n```\n"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":32021,"output":695,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32716,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775088207000}}
